  }, `Carter arrived in Hollywood in October 1939. Based on the mention of his arrival in African American newspapers, Carter was already a nationally known actor in black entertainment. The California Eagle, for example, ran an article titled, “Jack Carter Here for RKO Role” in their October 26th 1939 issue:`), React.createElement(MDXTag, {
